snippet.title: Abyss Fantasia - Official Trailer | TGS 2023
snippet.description:
In the city of Cynthia, the young girl Eucaly, in order to find her lost past, steps into the abyss at the edge of the city. Along the way, she will experience complex and treacherous emotions, encounter various strange creatures, and finally uncover the deepest secrets of the Abyss.
Steam Store Page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1985940/Abyss_Fantasia/
